<h1>Welcome to AAACT</h1>

<p>This is the starter home page for the Digital Accessibility and Inclusive Design (DAID) team.</p>

<h2>What is DAID?</h2>

<p>Digital Accessibility and Inclusive Design focuses on creating accessible digital experiences for all users. We prioritize inclusive design from the ground up.</p>

<h3>Our Focus Areas</h3>

<ul>
  <li>Web accessibility (WCAG 2.1 AA compliance)</li>
  <li>Digital design standards and guidelines</li>
  <li>Inclusive user experience practices</li>
  <li>Awareness and training</li>
</ul>

